Please Search Google Play for XOTHEMES and browse for the matching themes.  It allows users to have fun changing the look of their Text, SMS or Chat interface on their Android phones.   â¥ CLICK HERE for XOTHEMES and browse for the matching themes. Instructions:  Please Click OPEN and Follow OnScreen Directions Or apply from within GO SMS Pro.  Pop Up customization:To have Pop Up working properly:1) Click Menu/Theme/GO Popup/TurnOn/ 2) now click on a little setting icon on upper right corner(3 little bars), choose use the normal popup. click back. Done.Need more HELP? Please send an Email to ten.designer@gmail.comâ¥ Want a different FREE theme?  - No Problem!!    Please Search GOOGLE PLAY for XOTHEMES- We have over 150 themes available. About XOthemes:Â (1) We add New Themes DAILY, follow us http://www.twitter.com/@xo_studio(2) Click on More by Developer in this page to see more themes(3) More Screenshots of our themes at our website http://xothemes.blogspot.comAbout our design:Â Do you Love Zebra theme, wild animal print for your Go SMS PRO, GO CONTACTS or GO Launcher EX?
